{"tid":560343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨丸骾喉：與死神搏鬥26天　8歲女童離世","createTime":"2018-02-14T04:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T08:25:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1be8ef00e542227e87c380a1017765604cae53","tid":560343,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"食墨魚丸骾喉昏迷8歲女生，在醫院搶救26天後不治。上月18日，元朗欖口村路佛教陳榮根紀念學校一名就讀小三的姓周（8歲）女生，趁小息時間，在小食部購買墨魚丸進食。期間，懷疑因為上課鐘聲響起，她心急排隊邊行邊食，匆忙吞嚥致骾喉窒息，當場暈倒操場內，有教職員趕至急救，惟她被送院搶救之後，一直陷入昏迷，情況危殆，家人憂心忡忡，每天在病房守候打氣，惜周女與死神搏鬥26天後，至本周一(12日)下午3時53分，終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214112037242-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180214%2Fbkn-20180214112037242-0214_00822_001.html&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2B5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9eb01db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180214/bkn-20180214112037242-0214_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ad40d77379d08f79fcd350b7ce1e7837417d36","tid":560343,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:40:35.000Z","msg":"命也"},{"pid":"9e8c280b7e08718aa56cae2d26b8d95a553910f5","tid":560343,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890b9f4ce100346fb2ebe54b152f4c11bdcec801","tid":560343,"uid":164070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"26天<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2413c358d8cfacd7a028f2673f5f91ac715d0b63","tid":560343,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e132ecb76b57b1b97fea2487b005de46f4d7d1e6","ti